}}'''2020年捷克公寓火灾'''發生於2020年8月8日，在距离[[捷克|捷克]]首都[[布拉格|布拉格]]仅300公里的[[博胡明|博胡明]]Nerudova街的13层楼高的公寓发生大火，造成11名居民死亡，其中包括3名儿童。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Police: 10 killed in apartment fire in the Czech Republic|url=https://www.journal-news.com/news/nation-world/police-10-killed-in-apartment-fire-in-the-czech-republic/AV7XIXQJ6RDMBPLQKMKP3G3NFY/|accessdate=2020-08-09|work=journal-news|language=en}}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-08-08|title=Czech apartment fire kills 11, including three children - iDNES.cz|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-czech-fire-idUKKCN2540V6|accessdate=2020-08-09|archive-date=2020-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816105012/https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-czech-fire-idUKKCN2540V6|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Several killed in Czech apartment building fire, suspect arrested|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/killed-czech-apartment-building-fire-suspect-arrested-200808173943552.html|accessdate=2020-08-09|work=www.aljazeera.com|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921190703/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/killed-czech-apartment-building-fire-suspect-arrested-200808173943552.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>此次火災是[[捷克|捷克共和国]]历史上最严重的火灾事件<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-08-08|title=Eleven people killed in Czech Republic apartment building fire|language=en-GB|work=euronews|url=https://www.euronews.com/2020/08/08/eleven-people-killed-in-czech-republic-apartment-building-fire|accessdate=2020-08-09|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020161034/https://www.euronews.com/2020/08/08/eleven-people-killed-in-czech-republic-apartment-building-fire|dead-url=no}}</ref>。发生火灾的建筑物隸屬於{{cs-link|博胡明市政廳|Architektonický komplex budovy radnice (Bohumín)}}。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tragédie v Bohumíně. Požár paneláku nepřežilo jedenáct lidí, mezi oběťmi jsou i tři děti {{!}} Domov|url=https://www.lidovky.cz/domov/tragedie-v-bohumine-pozar-panelaku-neprezilo-jedenact-lidi-mezi-obetmi-jsou-i-tri-deti.A200808_184934_ln_domov_sei|accessdate=2020-08-09|date=2020-08-08|work=Lidovky.cz|language=cs|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108094315/https://www.lidovky.cz/domov/tragedie-v-bohumine-pozar-panelaku-neprezilo-jedenact-lidi-mezi-obetmi-jsou-i-tri-deti.A200808_184934_ln_domov_sei|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==事故==
根据[[摩拉維亞-西里西亞州|摩拉維亞-西里西亞州]]州长{{cs-link|馮德拉克|Ivo Vondrák}}的說法，8月8日晚上约6點40分，公寓着火，第11层楼全部被燒毁。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Deadly fire at Czech apartment block, arson suspected {{!}} DW {{!}} 08.08.2020|url=https://www.dw.com/en/deadly-fire-at-czech-apartment-block-arson-suspected/a-54499786|accessdate=2020-08-09|author=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|work=DW.COM|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029105438/https://www.dw.com/en/deadly-fire-at-czech-apartment-block-arson-suspected/a-54499786|dead-url=no}}</ref>据报道，有6人在大火中遇难，另有5人为躲避大火从11楼的公寓阳台跳下遇难，其中還包括一只宠物狗。<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-08-09|title=Eleven die in fire in Czech Republic tower block|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-53711133|accessdate=2020-08-09|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009205057/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-53711133|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Multiple residents killed in Czech Republic apartment fire|url=https://www.smh.com.au/world/europe/multiple-residents-killed-in-czech-republic-apartment-fire-20200809-p55jzq.html|accessdate=2020-08-09|date=2020-08-09|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027204928/https://www.smh.com.au/world/europe/multiple-residents-killed-in-czech-republic-apartment-fire-20200809-p55jzq.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>另外十人受伤，其中包括两名消防员以及一名警察<ref>{{Cite web|title=捷克30年最致命火災11死10傷！　跳樓逃生全摔死…警逮1名縱火犯|url=https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200809/1780386.htm|accessdate=|author=東森新聞雲|date=|format=|publisher=|language=}}</ref>。

据报道，捷克内政部长{{en-link|哈馬切克|Jan Hamáček}}表示此次火災是一起人為纵火，是由于长期的邻里纠纷所造成的<ref>{{Cite news|author=Press|first=The Associated|date=2020-08-08|title=11 Killed, 10 Injured in Czech Republic Apartment Fire|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2020/08/08/world/europe/ap-eu-czech-fire.html|accessdate=2020-08-09|issn=0362-4331}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=11 killed in suspected arson at Czech apartment block|url=https://alkhaleejtoday.co/international/5028966/11-killed-in-suspected-arson-at-Czech-apartment-block.html|accessdate=2020-08-09|date=2020-08-09|work=AlKhaleej Today|language=ar}}</ref>。警方拘留了一名與縱火有關的的嫌疑人。<ref name=":0" />

